# TailwindCSS Rules v1.0.0

## Best Practices

### 1. Class Organization
```tsx
<div className="flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500 text-white">
```

### 2. Responsive Design
```tsx
<div className="flex flex-col md:flex-row lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3">
```

### 3. Custom Colors
- Define custom colors in tailwind.config.js
- Use semantic names: primary, secondary, accent

## Restrictions

- ❌ No inline styles
- ❌ No custom CSS unless necessary
- ❌ No arbitrary values (`w-[123px]`)